<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-8589] url.getPort returning -1, needs additional check</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-8589</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In our environment, the camel-swagger component is building relative urls with a port of -1. &lt;a href=&quot;http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/net/URL.html#getPort(&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/net/URL.html#getPort(&lt;/a&gt;) is what is returning -1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix is to change&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;      if (url.getPort != 80) {&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;to&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;      if (url.getPort != 80 &amp;amp;&amp;amp; url.getPort != -1) {&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;in RestSwaggerApiDeclarationServlet.scala. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/camel-2.15.x/components/camel-swagger/src/main/scala/org/apache/camel/component/swagger/RestSwaggerApiDeclarationServlet.scala#L111&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/camel-2.15.x/components/camel-swagger/src/main/scala/org/apache/camel/component/swagger/RestSwaggerApiDeclarationServlet.scala#L111&lt;/a&gt; for the line of code that is affected.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
